		<td><b>chr bankswitching with 8k chr ram?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />(rewriting question...)
<br />Does any game which uses 8k of CHR RAM <strong>(and no other chr ram/rom)</strong> do CHR bankswitching within the 8k?  It would be quite silly to do so, since it's just rearranging the same memory into a different configuration, but do any games do it?  The Waixing DQ4 pirate breaks if you emulate the MMC3 CHR bankswitching to change the mapping of CHR ram.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


