	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Lagrange Point is the first game that comes to mind.
<br />Pin-Bot/High Speed also switch their CHR RAM, but they have 64KB of CHR ROM in addition.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
