<br />edit:
<br />TQROM games have more than 8k of total chr memory.  I re-edited my post to bolden that restriction.  Does lagrange point only have 8k of chr ram?  Wow.  It sure fooled me, looked like it had at least 16k, until I carefully examined it under fceuxd, indeed it has 8k.

		

